thread.title: Chuck Duncan
thread.title_full: Security Camera Warehouse reviewed by Chuck Duncan

author: Chuck Duncan
title: Chuck Duncan
text: Staff was very helpful. Came in under budget because of the layout design by them. Used fewer cameras than expected. One critique: Would suggest making the approval for the floor plan layout easier to do. Printing and scanning the release form is tedious. This should be all online.
